        "description": "Physical test apparatus operates under ISO 14243-1 displacement-controlled protocol. Load cell calibration traceable to NIST. Test temperature 37 ± 1 °C in bovine serum lubricant. Five gait phases replicated. Gradation 2 minimum; Gradation 3 achieved through full traceability documentation and environmental control records."
