      },
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening model parameters (E = 945 MPa, σ_y = 21 MPa, E_t = 120 MPa) sourced from Kurtz et al. (2005) material characterisation study on GUR 1020. Penalty contact formulation validated against Hertzian analytical solution: peak pressure error 1.8%. Model form uncertainty included in Monte Carlo UQ as ±5% perturbation on elastic modulus. Gradation 3 achieved."
