        "description": "FE model boundary conditions (load magnitude, displacement profile, contact geometry) confirmed to match physical test apparatus settings within measurement uncertainty. Any differences quantified and their effect on QoI bounded. Gradation 2 minimum; Gradation 3 achieved when all differences are quantified and shown to contribute < 2% to QoI variation."
      },
